<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وسعيد بن المسيَّب <span class="c2">(٧)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>/ ٦١/ وعُرْوة بن الزُّبَير <span class="c2">(٨)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
